10
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:10,430
will surely witness our time
of prosperity and splendor.

11
00:02:17,920 --> 00:02:22,070
Time... patience...

12
00:02:31,670 --> 00:02:33,930
Oh, ancestors...

13
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:38,760
I am not a competent chieftain.

14
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:42,000
Yang Minghua has rebelled.

15
00:02:44,140 --> 00:02:45,720
Lei Hong has rebelled.

16
00:02:47,579 --> 00:02:49,250
Yuanzhou has rebelled.

17
00:02:50,700 --> 00:02:52,820
And the North Clan invaded.

18
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,750
So many territories have been lost.

19
00:02:57,720 --> 00:03:00,060
Zichuan has come to this state...

20
00:03:00,080 --> 00:03:04,810
It's... it's my fault.

21
00:03:09,180 --> 00:03:11,840
I absolutely cannot let the Zichuan family

22
00:03:12,580 --> 00:03:14,860
fall at my hands.

23
00:03:14,980 --> 00:03:17,260
And I can't let Ning

24
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:22,260
be left with nothing when she inherits.

25
00:03:24,010 --> 00:03:24,730
My Lord.

26
00:03:39,490 --> 00:03:42,740
Di Lin, you're right.

27
00:03:44,070 --> 00:03:47,540
What does it matter if I bear
eternal infamy?

28
00:03:47,980 --> 00:03:50,590
Compared to the survival of our family,

29
00:03:51,980 --> 00:03:54,180
the honor or disgrace of either of us...

30
00:03:55,860 --> 00:03:57,630
is insignificant.

31
00:04:01,170 --> 00:04:04,940
Like a phoenix reborn from ashes,
rising through fire.

32
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:12,210
Let's do... as you said.

33
00:04:17,430 --> 00:04:18,160
Yes, My Lord.

34
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:01,520
I can't die.

35
00:05:08,610 --> 00:05:10,290
My Yuanzhou.

36
