My Yuanzhou.

39
00:05:21,390 --> 00:05:22,710
My Yuanzhou.

40
00:05:52,370 --> 00:05:53,170
Yuanzhou.

41
00:06:08,890 --> 00:06:09,860
Yuanzhou.

42
00:06:10,690 --> 00:06:11,660
Yuanzhou.

43
00:06:16,340 --> 00:06:17,710
My Yuanzhou.

44
00:06:40,610 --> 00:06:43,780
My Yuanzhou!

45
00:06:58,600 --> 00:07:02,000
Yuanzhou City is gone!

46
00:07:04,530 --> 00:07:07,130
Yuanzhou is gone.

47
00:07:10,180 --> 00:07:15,030
My Yuanzhou City is no more.

48
00:07:33,480 --> 00:07:36,770
Everything happened so suddenly,
and I rushed here too hastily.

49
00:07:36,770 --> 00:07:37,830
Please forgive me.

50
00:07:37,830 --> 00:07:38,630
It's alright.

51
00:07:40,230 --> 00:07:40,870
Let's go.

52
00:07:41,420 --> 00:07:42,090
Wait.

53
00:07:49,110 --> 00:07:50,200
Princess of the North Clan,

54
00:07:50,200 --> 00:07:52,260
do you treat my residence as nothing?

55
00:07:52,710 --> 00:07:54,440
Coming and going as you please?

56
00:07:55,170 --> 00:07:56,100
I won't allow it.

57
00:07:56,560 --> 00:07:58,830
Your Highness, we must consider
the bigger picture.

58
00:07:58,830 --> 00:07:59,620
Ning, I...

59
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,260
If you want to leave...

60
00:08:03,450 --> 00:08:05,510
you must get through my three trials.

61
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:10,480
I'll wait for you outside.

62
00:08:23,900 --> 00:08:25,300
On the night we first met,

63
00:08:25,760 --> 00:08:27,220
we drank until dawn broke.

64
00:08:28,930 --> 00:08:32,130
Today, we shall also bid farewell
to each other with wine.

65
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:56,820
Princess Ning usually wants to
eat something after drinking.

66
00:08:57,440 --> 00:08:59,240
Mei, don't forget to prepare it.

67
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:12,440
When you first arrived in
the Imperial Capital...

68
00:09:12,470 --> 00:09:15,080
you often missed the cuisine
of your homeland.

69
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:23,700
Today, I've prepared delicacies
from the Imperial Capital for you.

70
00:09:23,700 --> 00:09:24,790
You must eat them

71
00:09:25,580 --> 00:09:28,180
and never forget them for the rest
of your life.

72
00:09:38,610 --> 00:09:40,650
This is delicious, try it.

73
00:09:46,100 --> 00:09:47,440
I carefully picked it.

74
00:09:47,610 --> 00:09:49,070
Of course it's delicious.

75
00:09:58,540 --> 00:10:01,270
This handkerchief is the one you used...

76
00:10:03,280 --> 00:10:06,880
to wipe away wood shavings when you
first entered the residence.

77
00:10:11,390 --> 00:10:12,560
Our friendship...

78
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,640
began with that misunderstanding.

79
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,260
After we part today...

80
00:10:53,590 --> 00:10:54,990
we will be enemies.

81
00:10:58,180 --> 00:11:00,980
Today, I tear this handkerchief
to break our bond.

82
00:11:01,460 --> 00:11:03,040
We are no longer friends.

83
00:11:11,480 --> 00:11:12,630
In my heart...

84
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:16,050
you'll always be my friend.

85
00:11:24,340 --> 00:11:28,540
One day, the North Clan and Zichuan

86
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,860
will also become friends.

87
00:12:11,360 --> 00:12:12,960
I'll ride ahead to Gray River

88
00:12:13,100 --> 00:12:14,050
to handle important matters.

89
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:16,380
Be extra careful escorting the Princess.

90
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:40,210
Di Lin!

91
00:12:43,870 --> 00:12:45,030
[Lin Xiujia]

92
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:49,800
Xiujia.

93
00:12:50,850 --> 00:12:51,490
Xiujia.

94
00:12:58,040 --> 00:13:00,040
I came back in such a hurry this time.

95
00:13:16,540 --> 00:13:18,140
I thought you might be angry.

96
00:13:23,920 --> 00:13:26,620
Though you look a bit weathered,
you haven't grown thin.

97
00:13:26,620 --> 00:13:27,990
Looks like you've listened to me.

98
00:13:27,990 --> 00:13:30,520
I thought I wouldn't see you
on this trip back.

99
00:13:30,950 --> 00:13:32,810
Lord Canxing has treated me well.

100
00:13:32,990 --> 00:13:34,450
Knowing that your visit would be brief,

101
00:13:34,450 --> 00:13:36,450
he hurried to send me here to see you.

102
00:13:37,400 --> 00:13:40,800
I won't need to return to
the Chieftain's Mansion after this.

103
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:48,890
Lord Canxing is indeed thoughtful.

104
00:13:52,240 --> 00:13:53,830
Though I don't know the specifics,

105
00:13:53,830 --> 00:13:56,370
I assume you're taking on
another important mission.

106
00:13:56,370 --> 00:13:58,370
But don't forget what I've told you.

107
00:13:58,710 --> 00:13:59,840
I remember them all.

108
00:14:00,830 --> 00:14:02,090
I will come back alive.

109
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:08,590
Our child and I will watch you
mount your horse.

110
00:14:08,700 --> 00:14:09,630
Don't look back.

111
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:11,540
Let him see his father

112
00:14:11,560 --> 00:14:12,890
in all his heroic glory.

113
00:14:29,780 --> 00:14:30,840
Wait for my return.

114
00:15:34,690 --> 00:15:36,180
From this day forth,

115
00:15:38,330 --> 00:15:43,500
cease... all warfare with the North Clan.

116
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:55,050
I've already dispatched Di Lin to Payi
for peace talks.

117
00:15:56,810 --> 00:15:58,780
We will return Princess Ka Dan

118
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:05,090
and hand over the jurisdiction
of the 23 districts in Yuanzhou.

119
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:08,260
We can't do it, My Lord.

120
00:16:08,620 --> 00:16:10,080
We absolutely can't do it.

121
00:16:11,550 --> 00:16:13,170
My mind is made up.

122
00:16:14,310 --> 00:16:16,120
No more discussion.

123
00:16:18,510 --> 00:16:19,260
My Lord.

124
00:16:20,350 --> 00:16:23,510
Yuanzhou is Zichuan's last line
of defense.

125
00:16:23,860 --> 00:16:25,190
One falls, and the other suffers.

126
00:16:25,190 --> 00:16:28,120
If we lose Yuanzhou, Zichuan will
be in grave danger!

127
00:16:28,340 --> 00:16:30,870
If we mobilize our
entire clan's strength...

128
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:39,080
and fight again, we'll lose everything,
not just Yuanzhou.

129
00:16:41,210 --> 00:16:42,940
No need to persuade me further.

130
00:16:46,460 --> 00:16:50,520
My Lord! If we don't fight
with all we have,

131
00:16:51,260 --> 00:16:54,380
how can we face the people of Yuanzhou?

132
00:16:54,960 --> 00:16:59,980
Speak again... after you understand
the war situation.

133
00:17:03,650 --> 00:17:05,170
It's too late.

134
00:17:08,900 --> 00:17:10,579
It's too late.

135
