It's too late.

136
00:17:16,220 --> 00:17:17,890
It's too late.

137
00:17:19,230 --> 00:17:20,270
My Lord!

138
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:23,960
My Lord!

139
00:17:25,450 --> 00:17:27,260
It's too late.

140
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,360
Di Lin...

141
00:17:54,610 --> 00:17:57,960
You disgraceful traitor who has yielded
and brought shame upon us.

142
00:17:57,960 --> 00:18:00,720
I ought to kill you with one stroke
of my sword!

143
00:18:08,510 --> 00:18:08,970
My Lord,

144
00:18:09,180 --> 00:18:11,490
we've launched dozens of attacks
on the city over the past few days,

145
00:18:11,490 --> 00:18:13,490
and our forces far outnumber theirs.

146
00:18:13,490 --> 00:18:14,120
It's just

147
00:18:14,350 --> 00:18:16,000
that they seem to be bewitched.

148
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:17,060
Every time they kill,

149
00:18:17,060 --> 00:18:18,270
their eyes turn blood-red.

150
00:18:18,270 --> 00:18:19,470
Don't talk nonsense.

151
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:22,310
We've been unable to take Payi City
for so long.

152
00:18:22,310 --> 00:18:24,670
The Divine Emperor is watching us
from the rear!

153
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:27,170
We must take Payi.

154
00:18:37,070 --> 00:18:39,400
Prepare to attack the city
at 3 AM tonight.

155
00:18:39,510 --> 00:18:41,980
No horses, everyone moves stealthily.

156
00:18:42,260 --> 00:18:43,310
No siege ladders,

157
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,680
bring only ropes.

158
00:18:44,800 --> 00:18:47,480
This time, the goal isn't to
breach the city

159
00:18:47,990 --> 00:18:49,590
but to shatter their spirit.

160
00:18:49,930 --> 00:18:51,130
I want captives.

161
00:18:51,310 --> 00:18:52,510
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

162
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:09,030
Eat something.

163
00:19:11,090 --> 00:19:11,850
I'm good.

164
00:19:15,420 --> 00:19:17,480
Eating at this time makes one drowsy.

165
00:19:18,880 --> 00:19:20,010
This is also the time

166
00:19:20,220 --> 00:19:22,620
when people's willpower is at its weakest.

167
00:19:23,570 --> 00:19:24,530
Our opponents

168
00:19:24,900 --> 00:19:27,100
also prefer to attack the city
at this time.

169
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:28,460
You should still eat something.

170
00:19:28,460 --> 00:19:30,060
To replenish your strength.

171
00:19:32,450 --> 00:19:34,980
I'll eat half, and you can
have the other half.

172
00:19:50,300 --> 00:19:50,820
Ze.

173
00:19:52,160 --> 00:19:54,750
Why don't you tell us another story

174
00:19:55,000 --> 00:19:56,880
about the girls from Chunfeng Garden?

175
00:19:56,880 --> 00:19:59,720
My Lord, the stories about the girls

176
00:20:00,390 --> 00:20:01,540
must be saved and told sparingly.

177
00:20:01,540 --> 00:20:02,420
Come on.

178
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:04,920
War is the way of deception.

179
00:20:05,190 --> 00:20:07,190
The men are thinking about home now.

180
00:20:07,230 --> 00:20:09,880
Their families... and sweethearts.

181
00:20:11,390 --> 00:20:13,520
Then I don't even need to tell stories.

182
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:14,560
Just a song,

183
00:20:14,710 --> 00:20:18,040
and it'll cure your lovesickness.

184
00:20:21,780 --> 00:20:31,180
♪ Sleep eludes me past midnight,
as osmanthu drifts through the air ♪

185
00:20:32,530 --> 00:20:43,490
♪ Your lightly furrowed brows
still linger in my mind ♪

186
