♪ I remove my heavy armor ♪

187
00:20:50,960 --> 00:20:55,380
♪ And take off the weary mask I wore ♪

188
00:20:56,790 --> 00:21:01,880
♪ By the lamplight, knees drawn close,
we speak of a dream ♪

189
00:21:03,280 --> 00:21:07,380
♪ We drink and laugh till morning gleams ♪

190
00:22:15,230 --> 00:22:16,750
Everyone, prepare for battle!

191
00:22:16,750 --> 00:22:17,950
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

192
00:23:03,390 --> 00:23:04,150
Maocai!

193
00:23:07,610 --> 00:23:08,970
Maocai!

194
00:23:25,190 --> 00:23:26,450
Attention, everyone!

195
00:23:26,630 --> 00:23:28,020
Guard the city walls closely!

196
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,480
Don't let your guard down!

197
00:23:29,580 --> 00:23:30,780
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

198
00:23:50,130 --> 00:23:53,000
Get off! Quickly! Don't move!

199
00:23:53,430 --> 00:23:55,870
Maocai!

200
00:23:56,370 --> 00:23:56,960
Maocai!

201
00:23:56,990 --> 00:23:57,840
Maocai!

202
00:24:00,230 --> 00:24:00,870
Maocai!

