♪ Sleep eludes me past midnight,
as osmanthu drifts through the air ♪

204
00:24:50,710 --> 00:25:00,500
♪ Your lightly furrowed brows
still linger in my mind ♪

205
00:25:01,300 --> 00:25:10,820
♪ We met in silence past midnight,
the moon hung in the east ♪

206
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:17,150
♪ Robes still in disarray ♪

207
00:25:17,630 --> 00:25:25,230
♪ Silken strands draped across
both shoulders ♪

208
00:25:26,340 --> 00:25:35,950
♪ As the candle flickers out at dawn,
her lips still tinged with red ♪

209
00:25:36,500 --> 00:25:41,100
♪ Spring breeze returns, gentle as ever ♪

210
00:25:41,470 --> 00:25:50,260
♪ The sun rises and sets once more ♪

211
00:26:02,540 --> 00:26:07,110
♪ I remove my heavy armor ♪

212
00:26:07,950 --> 00:26:10,100
It feels great to be part of a group!

213
00:26:08,770 --> 00:26:12,770
♪ And take off the weary mask I wore ♪

214
00:26:14,150 --> 00:26:19,140
♪ By the lamplight, knees drawn close,
we speak of a dream ♪

215
00:26:20,540 --> 00:26:24,840
♪ We drink and laugh till morning gleams ♪

216
00:26:25,550 --> 00:26:29,620
♪ Your torch still burns bright ♪

217
00:26:29,780 --> 00:26:30,870
Brothers!

218
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:36,000
♪ Lighting that rugged path
through the cold night ♪

219
00:26:32,330 --> 00:26:37,010
Keep... singing the song!

220
00:26:37,050 --> 00:26:42,250
♪ Where we once parted ways ♪

221
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,430
I have to go save him.

222
00:26:40,780 --> 00:26:43,540
Let me go! I have to save him!

223
00:26:43,440 --> 00:26:48,150
♪ Glory remains engraved ♪

224
00:26:44,500 --> 00:26:46,470
Let me go! Zichuan Xiu!

225
00:26:48,830 --> 00:26:53,660
♪ The friend who vanished from view ♪

226
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:55,020
I'm going home first.

227
00:26:54,350 --> 00:26:58,520
♪ Was never truly gone ♪

228
00:26:56,820 --> 00:26:58,640
Let me go!

229
00:27:00,480 --> 00:27:07,530
♪ I stayed silent, just waiting
for your voice ♪

230
00:27:01,980 --> 00:27:02,710
Father.

231
00:27:06,300 --> 00:27:07,100
I'm sorry.

232
00:27:19,220 --> 00:27:20,460
-Maocai!
-Maocai!

233
00:27:58,760 --> 00:27:59,490
Who's there?

234
00:28:09,250 --> 00:28:09,870
Stop!

235
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:12,890
I'm a messenger from the Zichuan family!

236
00:28:12,890 --> 00:28:15,290
I seek an audience
with the Divine Emperor!

237
00:28:15,800 --> 00:28:16,630
Stop!

238
00:28:35,100 --> 00:28:36,580
Why don't you fight back?

239
00:28:36,780 --> 00:28:38,040
I'm here to negotiate,

240
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:39,380
not to fight.

241
00:28:50,550 --> 00:28:52,070
You've got some guts.

242
00:28:53,900 --> 00:28:56,630
No wonder you dared to enter
the enemy camp alone.

243
00:28:57,430 --> 00:28:58,470
What's your name?

244
00:29:00,080 --> 00:29:04,670
Ge Qing, Captain of the Royal Escorts
of the Zichuan family,

245
00:29:05,820 --> 00:29:07,520
requests an audience
with the Divine Emperor.

246
00:29:07,520 --> 00:29:09,720
Please inform His Majesty on my behalf.

247
00:29:10,340 --> 00:29:12,470
During my time in seclusion
and reflection,

248
00:29:12,470 --> 00:29:14,420
I re-read the historical records

249
00:29:14,730 --> 00:29:16,150
as Father instructed and reviewed

250
00:29:16,150 --> 00:29:17,950
all the major and minor battles.

251
00:29:18,320 --> 00:29:19,390
[Ka Dun, Eldest Prince of the North Clan]

252
00:29:19,260 --> 00:29:20,590
Learning from history,

253
00:29:20,710 --> 00:29:22,640
I've reflected on my past mistakes

254
00:29:22,660 --> 00:29:23,490
[Lu Di]

255
00:29:22,740 --> 00:29:25,390
and I've also gained some insights.

256
00:29:27,020 --> 00:29:30,430
Then tell me, what's your view
on the current war situation?

257
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:36,600
The siege of Payi has dragged on
without success,

258
00:29:36,600 --> 00:29:38,950
preventing us from striking at their core.

259
00:29:38,950 --> 00:29:42,750
However, we can gradually devour Yuanzhou
to expand our territory!

260
00:29:44,430 --> 00:29:46,950
Father, I was just careless at that time.

261
00:29:47,230 --> 00:29:48,410
This time, with renewed determination,

262
00:29:48,410 --> 00:29:49,910
I absolutely won't be arrogant
or impatient.

263
00:29:49,910 --> 00:29:52,630
Please give me another chance, Father.

264
00:29:53,580 --> 00:29:55,230
Then in your opinion,

265
00:29:55,380 --> 00:29:57,640
how long would it take to take down Wayun?

266
00:30:00,910 --> 00:30:02,510
Three months, Your Majesty!

267
00:30:03,340 --> 00:30:04,870
I, Lu Di, am willing to assist
His Highness

268
00:30:04,870 --> 00:30:06,910
in crushing Yuanzhou and seizing Wayun

269
00:30:06,910 --> 00:30:08,190
within three months!

